LurpicUI bundle layout

Build tree staging root:
  @LURPIC_BUNDLE_STAGE_ROOT@

Staged subdirectories:
  examples: @LURPIC_BUNDLE_EXAMPLES_DIR@
  themes:   @LURPIC_BUNDLE_THEMES_DIR@
  docs:     @LURPIC_BUNDLE_DOCS_DIR@
  presets:  @LURPIC_BUNDLE_PRESETS_DIR@

Later install-tree layout:
  examples: share/lurpic/examples
  themes:   share/lurpic/themes
  docs:     share/lurpic/docs
  presets:  share/lurpic/presets

Policy:
  CMake may stage generated example/theme artifacts into the build tree.
  Source trees are never mutated by build targets.
